uences (lazy).</p></li><li><p class="paragraph">Various utilities for working with strings and char sequences.</p></li><li><p class="paragraph">Extensions for JDK classes making it convenient to work with files, IO, and threading.</p></li></ul></div><div class="content sourceset-dependent-content" data-togglable=":kotlin-stdlib_2.3_latest/wasm-wasi"><h2 class="">Kotlin Standard Library</h2><p class="paragraph">The Kotlin Standard Library provides living essentials for everyday work with Kotlin. These include:</p><ul><li><p class="paragraph">Higher-order functions implementing idiomatic patterns (<a href="kotlin/let.html">let</a>, <a href="kotlin/apply.html">apply</a>, kotlin.io.use, kotlin.synchronized, etc).</p></li><li><p class="paragraph">Extension functions providing querying operations for collections (eager) and sequences (lazy).</p></li><li><p class="paragraph">Various utilities for working with strings and char sequences.</p></li><li><p class="paragraph">Extensions for JDK classes making it convenient to work with files, IO, and threading.</p></li></ul></div>    </div>
